{"tid":702741,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"話陳嘉欣素顏似師奶巨躉女神幻滅     寫呢篇新聞既一定係女人","createTime":"2018-06-15T07:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T13:02:02.000Z","uid":60281,"like":167,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"54b56c5196ec14edaeca21f327c961b17c41de3f","tid":702741,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"明明素顏同平時差唔多，巨躉又正，何來女神幻滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/150341_f05d5765d5ba73d54accd7197ae89470.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F150341_f05d5765d5ba73d54accd7197ae89470.png&h=ee90fd79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180615/2_593067_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F2_593067_0&d=p4dHIbT8V34C17TamCL2X%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f44faafe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F2_593067_0&h=318cd408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180615/2_593067_0</a><br />\n<br />\n早前從一個女子背影，帶點師奶味的打扮，加上一個肥躉，實在很難想像呢個四眼妹，是網民至愛嘅主播女神嘉欣BB。 <br />\n<br />\n大台班女神主播，好似周嘉儀、陳嘉倩走得嘅走，張文采亦嫁人，網民開電視睇到，仲有個樣清清甜甜嘅陳嘉欣，有傳佢近年當上新聞部一姐，但一姐似乎唔多在意自己身形，從一身打扮，戴埋副眼鏡，師奶味重，同鏡頭前嘅嘉欣BB女神形象，真係有啲幻滅！ <br />\n<br />\n不過陳嘉欣今年都33歲，而且一向走平實路線，唔使上鏡時候，就真係一個好普通嘅中女。日前佢返廠錄影前，快快手手隊件三文治同咖啡，三扒兩撥就一餐，跟住就匆匆趕上公司車。咁又係，返工預番啲時間，化個女神靚妝先出鏡。"},{"pid":"2e66acbea6540cd9fa788458572c2b48c189638e","tid":702741,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58daff5ef5e9f7bc637b584d187df76ab1466ff","tid":702741,"uid":140769,"like":275,"dislike":2,"score":273,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14b643d8f6efff3ea53b31b2b89526b922f73ce","tid":702741,"uid":68081,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"呢D先係神級，個新聞記者擺明作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8ce40ec62170253f4f41ba94ad276607ad075c","tid":702741,"uid":143582,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"好正，個記者收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc9345eadcd32c4c9ee8f57a2b2946cfc0d0891","tid":702741,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"2967365ee0b16ffe8674858557a2164770b9713f","tid":702741,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"佢條仔勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed0520d5f6e664ec5a1b3c9f7f5a02666fbebff","tid":702741,"uid":152598,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"唇上汗毛 化妝都遮唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似鬍鬚"},{"pid":"6b1ede089c050221ca361b5a6725e70f228fee76","tid":702741,"uid":166474,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"係肥D，33歲中女算唔差"},{"pid":"c2bdc589c0f5cf5b4f479ae58783fe6ffb768f0d","tid":702741,"uid":37666,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTi